rows.label: tlk44400085_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I wish someone could reassure me that
things are going to turn out fine...

rows.label: tlk44400085_03_msg0002
rows.name:
But no, I'm sure we'll pull through. His
Majesty is still going strong, and our
Crown Prince has shown his mettle!

rows.label: tlk44400085_03_msg0003
rows.name:
If we continue to be as determined and
positive as His Highness Zeke, I'm sure
things will turn out just dandy.
